Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.92,0:44:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I am."\NAnd by grace you say, "So I'm short, fat
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.92,0:44:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ugly, and stupid\Nand broke." So,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.96,0:44:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was poor until I was 40. Hear all the\Npeople crying about being poverty. Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.40,0:44:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,right. You should know what poverty is.\NI was poor till 40. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.20,0:44:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so you live on $3 a week for food. So,\Nso,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.68,0:44:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so nothing.\NEvery time you catch your mind saying
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.64,0:44:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so, you say so. So what? So nothing.\NSo so and so is wrong. So
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.04,0:44:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he's wrong.\NSo So I'm wrong. So you're wrong. So
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.64,0:44:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,he's wrong. He was wrong.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.48,0:45:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way to get off blame is admit\Nyou were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.72,0:45:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it take? Nothing. You're lying\Nanyway. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.80,0:45:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of being polite.\NYou're wrong. Well, I must agree I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.52,0:45:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm looking at how you see it\Nand I see the value of it.
