Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.00,0:46:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It scares me a little. So, I try not to\Nlook at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.83,0:46:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's something's following me\Naround.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.20,0:47:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant paranoia. Yeah. H how did things\Ncome about? We said it's that which
