Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.07,0:47:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. When you get beyond cause and\Neffect and you see all is occurring by
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.40,0:47:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of the field is a\Nconsequence of what you are in the
