Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.52,0:47:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no nothing causing it. If\Nthere's nothing causing anything that's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.59,0:47:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,happening, then everything is happening\Nspontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.48,0:47:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the illusion is there's a you\Ncausing it to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.96,0:47:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any you. And if there was,\Nit's not causing it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.72,0:47:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's happening. So, you get to\Nenjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.59,0:48:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't decide to do that.\NWhat are you up to, you idiot? I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.40,0:48:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,know.\NEverything is just happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.68,0:48:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, you're completely and\Ntotally free because that what's that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.20,0:48:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which you are is what's determining\Nuh how you know what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.11,0:48:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh it's sort of a different paradigm.\NDifferent paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.92,0:48:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason science can't get what\Nconsciousness is about is because it's
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.92,0:48:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in a different paradigm\Nand it struggles hard. In fact, I read
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.04,0:48:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,these learn learned dissertations and\Nyou can hear the ego almost groaning
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.59,0:48:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with pain trying to push the intellect,\Nyou know, past 499.5,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.68,0:48:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't get it past there. You got\Nto you got to shift to a different
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.40,0:48:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,dimension.\NBut you see, you're talking to fish
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.11,0:48:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who've never experienced error. So, you\Nrealize that they don't get what you're
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.44,0:49:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,saying.\NThe average mind does not grasp paradigm
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.64,0:49:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or paradigm jump or contextualization.\NDoesn't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.52,0:49:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's say you're a fish. You've\Nalways been a fish. All your friends are
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.72,0:49:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,fish. Your family's been fish. In fact,\Nyou've been fish for millions of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.64,0:49:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All you know is water.\NSo if I say to a fish, tell me about
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.44,0:49:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,water. He'd say, what are you talking\Nabout?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? If I ask human beings, tell me\Nabout space, they tell you, what can I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.92,0:49:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,say about space?\NSo for the fish to be able to describe
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.68,0:49:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,water, it would have to experience\Nnonwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.35,0:49:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the more evolved fish fly out into\Nthe air and can go back and tell their
