Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.11,0:50:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,phosphorescent and uh fine fish kept\Ncoming out of the water and landing on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.28,0:50:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the deck and flopping around well you\Nsee when the fish come out of the water
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.52,0:50:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,like that this fish is not causing this\Nfish to come out of the water is it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.83,0:50:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,doing it spontaneously\Nas an expression of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.83,0:50:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So your thoughts are like these fish you\Nsee and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.72,0:50:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they're spontaneously coming out of\Nnothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.64,0:50:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The nothingness\Nin fact where the absolute certainty
