Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.28,0:50:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to a thought.\NWe said 99% of the we used to say it was
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.80,0:50:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,98% but maybe maybe things have\Nimproved. Now only 99% 99% of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.80,0:51:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is blank at all times. Only 1% is busy.\NUsed to be 2% now it's down to 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.88,0:51:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably we can squish it right down to\Nhalf a percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.76,0:51:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So people bemoan that they're at the\Neffect of the mind. No, you're not at
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.16,0:51:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the effect of the mind. 99% of the mind\Nis silent. Only 1% is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.31,0:51:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,\Nall you have to do is watch the 1%. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.35,0:51:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,what attracts your attention because you\Nbecome entranced by the 1% because it's
