Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.80,0:51:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's happening there, you think\Nthere's a you that's causing it to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.64,0:51:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,happen. No, no. Thinkingness is just\Nhappening. And if you want to find that
