Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.52,0:52:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh okay. So what's happened then is we\Nhave become we are in a hypnotic trance
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.55,0:52:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of the 1%.\NSee, you don't have to save 99 all 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.07,0:52:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of yourself. 1% is all you got to say.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.40,0:52:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's happened is we've come into a\Nhypnotic trance of the 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.83,0:52:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact. Resist. It's a fact. 99%\Nof your mind is already cleared away.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.92,0:52:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 1% you got to worry about.\NThat's feel better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.88,0:52:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to feel better. I like people\Nfeel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.20,0:52:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was 5 minutes late after\Nlunch. Then all the people that were
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.55,0:52:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,late wouldn't have to feel guilty.\NI was late just for you folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.11,0:53:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I 20 minutes late. That's something\Ndifferent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.55,0:53:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Npeople say well if I let go of my ego
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.59,0:53:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how will I survive?\NHow will who survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.92,0:53:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is destined to be will be. You\Nknow, so surrendering to God means
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.31,0:53:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,without the considerations.\NConsiderations
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.76,0:53:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,though many people are\Naligned with the truth except for the
