Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.40,0:53:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,then\Nthe intention manifests.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.24,0:53:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, what's happening is the mind\Nhas considerations
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.59,0:54:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,considerations.\NIt's not 100% in agreement with your
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.76,0:54:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,intention.\NLet's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.80,0:54:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual work then is finding out what\Nthose considerations are and being
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.35,0:54:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to let them go. People would\Nsay, "Well, I'm not willing to admit
